      *                                                               *
      *  MD058809 - After installation of MQ9 compatibility patch and *
      *             restart of the Meridian Replication subsystem     *
      *             REPMIDASPT, the job MPT1PBSIN ended in MSGW.      *
      *  artf44103 - Added field to record the intended length of the *
      *              target message.  This is necessary because a     *
      *              message can have blank fields at then end, and   *
      *              trimming the data in the RPG causes a message of *
      *              the wrong length to be sent, which confuses      *
      *              Meridian.  Similarly, sending the entire data    *
      *              from the RPG results in a message that is too    *
      *              long.                                            *
      *                                                               *
      *  CRP003 - New Functions                                       *
      *           Renaming Message Type                               *
      *           - New Message Type field added                      *
      *           Transfer of multiple files                          *
      *           - Processing Sequence field added                   *
      *           - source Table Name field added.                   *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     A          R RPAPCID0                  TEXT('(c) Misys International +
     A                                            Banking Systems Ltd. +
                                                  2001')

     A            RBMSGTYPE     32A         TEXT('Message Type')
                                            COLHDG('Message' +
                                                   'Type')
     A            RBADDPROC      1A         TEXT('Additional Processing Flag')
                                            COLHDG('Addn.' 'Proc.' +
                                                   'Flag')
     A            RBPROGRAM     10A         TEXT('Program to call')
                                            COLHDG('Program' 'to call')
      * Start changes for CRP003.
     A            RBNEWTYPE     32A         TEXT('New Message Type')
                                            COLHDG('New Message' +
                                                   'Type')
     A            RBPROCSEQ      2S 0       TEXT('Processing Sequence')
                                            COLHDG('Proc. Seq.')

      * N.B. RBTABLENAM is the name of an AS/400 file to be transferred
      *  in its entirety using the Replication command KMDDLC.
      * Strictly speaking this has nothing to do with this file but has
      *  been placed here purely for simplicity sake, files transferred
      *  in this way may well need extra processing to be performed.
     A            RBTABLENM     32A         TEXT('Name of file to be sent')
                                            COLHDG('Name of file')
      * End   changes for CRP003.

      * Start changes for artf44103
     A            RBTGTMSGLN     5S 0       TEXT('Length of target message')
     A                                      COLHDG('Target' 'Message' +
     A                                             'Length')

      * End   changes for artf44103

